<lb n="0560b10" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><title>餓鬼報應<note n="0560011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">經＝出雜藏經【宋】【宮】，經＋（出雜藏經）夾註【元】【明】</note><note n="0560011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">經【大】，出雜藏經【宋】【宮】，經(出雜藏經)【元】【明】</note><app n="0560011"><lem wit="【大】">經</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【宮】">出雜藏經</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">經<note place="inline">出雜藏經</note></rdg></app></title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0560b11" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0560b12" ed="T"/><byline cb:type="Translator">失<note n="0560012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">譯＋（人名）【明】</note><note n="0560012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">譯【大】，譯人名【明】</note><app n="0560012"><lem wit="【大】">譯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">譯人名</rdg></app><note n="0560013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔附東晉錄〕－【宮】</note><note n="0560013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">附東晉錄【大】，〔－〕【宮】</note><app n="0560013"><lem wit="【大】">附東晉錄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></byline>
<lb n="0560b13" ed="T"/><cb:div type="jing"><p xml:id="pT17p0560b1301">尊者大目揵連，從佛在耆闍崛山<note n="0560014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔中〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0560014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">中【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0560014"><lem wit="【大】">中</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>，遊<note n="0560015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔行〕－【三】</note><note n="0560015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">行【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0560015"><lem wit="【大】">行</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>
<lb n="0560b14" ed="T"/><note n="0560016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔恒〕－【宮】</note><note n="0560016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">恒【大】，〔－〕【宮】</note><app n="0560016"><lem wit="【大】">恒</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>水邊，見諸餓鬼甚多，受罪不同。見尊者
<lb n="0560b15" ed="T"/>目連，皆起敬心，來問因<note n="0560017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">緣＝由【三】【宮】</note><note n="0560017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">緣【大】，由【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0560017"><lem wit="【大】">緣</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">由</rdg></app>。</p><p xml:id="pT17p0560b1511" rend="inline">一鬼問言：「我常
<lb n="0560b16" ed="T"/>苦頭痛，不知何罪所致？」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0560b1610" rend="inline">目連答言：「汝本為人
<lb n="0560b17" ed="T"/>時，不能修<note n="0560018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">忍＝善【三】【宮】</note><note n="0560018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">忍【大】，善【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0560018"><lem wit="【大】">忍</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">善</rdg></app>，以杖打眾生頭，今受花報，果
<lb n="0560b18" ed="T"/>在地獄。」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0560b1804" rend="inline">一鬼問言：「我<note n="0560019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">常＋（患）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0560019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">常【大】，常患【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0560019"><lem wit="【大】">常</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">常患</rdg></app>瘡痛，何罪所致？」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0560b1816" rend="inline"><note n="0560020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（目連）＋答【三】【宮】</note><note n="0560020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">答【大】，目連答【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0560020"><lem wit="【大】">答</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">目連答</rdg></app>
<lb n="0560b19" ed="T"/>言：「汝為人時，無有慈心，焚燒山<note n="0560021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">野＝林【三】【宮】</note><note n="0560021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">野【大】，林【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0560021"><lem wit="【大】">野</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">林</rdg></app>，殘害眾
<lb n="0560b20" ed="T"/>生，今受花報，果在地獄。」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0560b2010" rend="inline">一鬼問言：「我舉身瘡
<lb n="0560b21" ed="T"/>爛，<note n="0560022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">不可堪忍＝痛不可堪【三】【宮】</note><note n="0560022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">不可堪忍【大】，痛不可堪【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0560022"><lem wit="【大】">不可堪忍</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">痛不可堪</rdg></app>，何罪所致？」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0560b2110" rend="inline">答言：「汝為人時，
<lb n="0560b22" ed="T"/><note n="0560023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">喜燂＝生燖【三】【宮】</note><note n="0560023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">喜燂【大】，生燖【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0560023"><lem wit="【大】">喜燂</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">生燖</rdg></app>猪羊，今受花報，果在地獄。」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0560b2213" rend="inline">一鬼問言：
<lb n="0560b23" ed="T"/>「我食<note n="0560024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">無足＝無有足時【三】【宮】</note><note n="0560024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">無足【大】，無有足時【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0560024"><lem wit="【大】">無足</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">無有足時</rdg></app>，初不得飽，何罪所致？」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0560b2313" rend="inline">答言：「汝為
<lb n="0560b24" ed="T"/>人時，<note n="0560025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">雖＝唯【宮】</note><note n="0560025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">雖【大】，唯【宮】</note><app n="0560025"><lem wit="【大】">雖</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">唯</rdg></app><note n="0560026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">飯＋（食）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0560026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">飯【大】，飯食【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0560026"><lem wit="【大】">飯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">飯食</rdg></app>眾生，<note n="0560027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">恒令不＝初不令【三】【宮】</note><note n="0560027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">恒令不【大】，初不令【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0560027"><lem wit="【大】">恒令不</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">初不令</rdg></app>足，今受花報，果
<lb n="0560b25" ed="T"/>在地獄。」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0560b2504" rend="inline">一鬼問言：「我<note n="0560028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔常〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0560028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">常【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0560028"><lem wit="【大】">常</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>苦頭痛，治之叵差，
<lb n="0560b26" ed="T"/>何罪所致？」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0560b2605" rend="inline">答言：「汝為人時，不敬道德，加以罵
<lb n="0560b27" ed="T"/>辱，今受花報，果在地獄」。</p><p xml:id="pT17p0560b2710" rend="inline">一鬼問言：「我生男女，
<lb n="0560b28" ed="T"/><note n="0560029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">盡皆＝皆悉【三】【宮】</note><note n="0560029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">盡皆【大】，皆悉【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0560029"><lem wit="【大】">盡皆</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">皆悉</rdg></app>端正<note n="0560030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔可愛〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0560030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">可愛【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0560030"><lem wit="【大】">可愛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>，而皆早死，念<note n="0560031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">無＝之【三】【宮】</note><note n="0560031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">無【大】，之【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0560031"><lem wit="【大】">無</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">之</rdg></app>斷絕，何
<lb n="0560b29" ed="T"/>罪所致？」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0560b2904" rend="inline">答言：「汝為人時，見<note n="0560032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">兒＝人【宮】</note><note n="0560032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">兒【大】，人【宮】</note><app n="0560032"><lem wit="【大】">兒</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">人</rdg></app>殺生，<note n="0560033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">助喜噉＝助其歡喜共噉其【三】【宮】</note><note n="0560033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">助喜噉【大】，助其歡喜共噉其【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0560033"><lem wit="【大】">助喜噉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">助其歡喜共噉其</rdg></app>
<pb n="0560c" ed="T" xml:id="T17.0746.0560c"/>
<lb n="0560c01" ed="T"/>肉，殺故<note n="0560034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">促＝短【三】【宮】</note><note n="0560034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">促【大】，短【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0560034"><lem wit="【大】">促</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">短</rdg></app>命，喜故痛毒，今受花報，果在地
<lb n="0560c02" ed="T"/>獄。」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0560c0202" rend="inline">一鬼問言：「我有一夫，而畜多婦，我應直
<lb n="0560c03" ed="T"/>宿，而不見納，何罪所致？」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0560c0310" rend="inline">答言：「汝為人時，不
<lb n="0560c04" ed="T"/>敬夫主，邪婬無禮，今受花報，果在地獄。」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0560c0416" rend="inline">一鬼
<lb n="0560c05" ed="T"/>問言：「我常頭痛，而男根瘡爛，何罪所致？」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0560c0516" rend="inline">答
<lb n="0560c06" ed="T"/>言：「汝為人時，於塔廟清淨之處行婬，今受花
<lb n="0560c07" ed="T"/>報，果在地獄。」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0560c0706" rend="inline">一鬼問言：「我得此身，麁澁不淨，
<lb n="0560c08" ed="T"/>何罪所致？」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0560c0805" rend="inline">答言：「汝為人時，不尊有德，輕賤善
<lb n="0560c09" ed="T"/>人，而以沙土<note n="0560035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">擲＝㩆【三】</note><note n="0560035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">擲【大】，㩆【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0560035"><lem wit="【大】">擲</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">㩆</rdg></app>坌沙門，今受花報，果在地
<lb n="0560c10" ed="T"/>獄。」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0560c1002" rend="inline">一鬼問言：「我食不啻一斛，而常不足，何罪
<lb n="0560c11" ed="T"/>所致？」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0560c1103" rend="inline">答言：「汝為人時，本作比丘，為僧求物，
<lb n="0560c12" ed="T"/>而以自食，今受花報，果在地獄。」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0560c1213" rend="inline">一鬼問言：「我
<lb n="0560c13" ed="T"/>受此形，脚腫項癭，何罪所致？」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0560c1312" rend="inline">答言：「汝為人
<lb n="0560c14" ed="T"/>時，使人及諸畜生負重無道，今受花報，果在
<lb n="0560c15" ed="T"/>地獄。」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0560c1503" rend="inline">一鬼問言：「我受此身，常患熱渴，何罪所
<lb n="0560c16" ed="T"/>致？」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0560c1602" rend="inline">答言：「汝為人時，喜好<note n="0560036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">漁獵＝獵魚【宋】，魚獵【宮】</note><note n="0560036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">漁獵【大】，獵魚【宋】，魚獵【宮】</note><app n="0560036"><lem wit="【大】">漁獵</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">獵魚</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">魚獵</rdg></app>，以所得魚，投
<lb n="0560c17" ed="T"/>之沙土，令其苦死，今受花報，果在地獄。」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0560c1716" rend="inline">一鬼
<lb n="0560c18" ed="T"/>問言：「我受此身，<note n="0560037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">狂癡＝癡狂【三】，常癡【宮】</note><note n="0560037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">狂癡【大】，癡狂【宋】【元】【明】，常癡【宮】</note><app n="0560037"><lem wit="【大】">狂癡</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">癡狂</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">常癡</rdg></app><note n="0560038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">無＝不【宋】</note><note n="0560038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">無【大】，不【宋】</note><app n="0560038"><lem wit="【大】">無</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">不</rdg></app><note n="0560039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">智＝知【三】【宮】</note><note n="0560039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">智【大】，知【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0560039"><lem wit="【大】">智</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">知</rdg></app>，何罪所致？」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0560c1815" rend="inline">答
<lb n="0560c19" ed="T"/>言：「汝為人時，以酒施人，今受花報，果在地獄。」</p>
<lb n="0560c20" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT17p0560c2001">一鬼問言：「我所生子，皆反噉我，何罪所致？」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0560c2017" rend="inline">答
<lb n="0560c21" ed="T"/>言：「汝為人時，不修孝養，今受花報，果在地獄。」</p>
<lb n="0560c22" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT17p0560c2201">一鬼問言：「我食常吐，何罪所致？」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0560c2213" rend="inline">答言：「汝為人
<lb n="0560c23" ed="T"/>時，有人中後索<note n="0560040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">食＋（者）【元】【明】【宮】</note><note n="0560040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">食【大】，食者【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0560040"><lem wit="【大】">食</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】【宮】">食者</rdg></app>，<note n="0560041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔汝〕－【宋】</note><note n="0560041" resp="CBETA" type="mod">汝【大】，〔－〕【宋】</note><app n="0560041"><lem wit="【大】">汝</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>瞋<note n="0560042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">罵＝詈【三】【宮】</note><note n="0560042" resp="CBETA" type="mod">罵【大】，詈【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0560042"><lem wit="【大】">罵</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">詈</rdg></app>而與，今受花
<lb n="0560c24" ed="T"/>報，果在地獄。」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0560c2406" rend="inline">一鬼問言：「我今一生資財無乏，
<lb n="0560c25" ed="T"/>而樂著弊<note n="0560043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">衣＝故【三】</note><note n="0560043" resp="CBETA" type="mod">衣【大】，故【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0560043"><lem wit="【大】">衣</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">故</rdg></app>，何罪所致？」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0560c2510" rend="inline">答言：「汝為人時，雖
<pb n="0561a" ed="T" xml:id="T17.0746.0561a"/>
<lb n="0561a01" ed="T"/>好布施，施後尋悔，今受花報，果在地獄。」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0561a0116" rend="inline">一鬼
<lb n="0561a02" ed="T"/>問言：「我<note n="0561001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">受＝今【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">受【大】，今【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561001"><lem wit="【大】">受</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">今</rdg></app>一形，恒倚巷陌，宿無常處，何罪
<lb n="0561a03" ed="T"/>所致？」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0561a0303" rend="inline">答言：「汝為人時，客來投止而不安隱，
<lb n="0561a04" ed="T"/>見他<note n="0561002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">容＝客【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">容【大】，客【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561002"><lem wit="【大】">容</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">客</rdg></app>止而復瞋罵，今受<note n="0561a0401" resp="CBETA" type="add">花【CB】【麗-CB】，華【大】</note><app n="0561a0401"><lem wit="【CB】【麗-CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">花<note type="cf1">K19n0763_p0739c11</note></lem><rdg wit="【大】">華</rdg></app>報，果在地獄。」</p>
<lb n="0561a05" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT17p0561a0501">一鬼問言：「我得此形，非男非女，何罪所致？」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0561a0517" rend="inline">答
<lb n="0561a06" ed="T"/>言：「汝為人時，而無慈心，好犍六畜，今受花報，
<lb n="0561a07" ed="T"/>果在地獄」。</p><p xml:id="pT17p0561a0705" rend="inline">一鬼問言：「我得此身，<note n="0561003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">躄＝癖【宋】</note><note n="0561003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">躄【大】，癖【宋】</note><app n="0561003"><lem wit="【大】">躄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">癖</rdg></app>不能行，
<lb n="0561a08" ed="T"/>何罪所致？」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0561a0805" rend="inline">答言：「汝為人時<note n="0561004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">好行＝自好【宮】</note><note n="0561004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">好行【大】，自好【宮】</note><app n="0561004"><lem wit="【大】">好行</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">自好</rdg></app>無道，拘繫
<lb n="0561a09" ed="T"/><note n="0561005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">人獸＝於人及以禽獸【三】，於人多畜禽獸【宮】</note><note n="0561005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">人獸【大】，於人及以禽獸【宋】【元】【明】，於人多畜禽獸【宮】</note><app n="0561005"><lem wit="【大】">人獸</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">於人及以禽獸</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">於人多畜禽獸</rdg></app>令不得行，今受花報，果在地獄。」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0561a0915" rend="inline">一鬼問
<lb n="0561a10" ed="T"/>言：「我此一身常患熱渴，行見恒河，清涼<note n="0561006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">美＝甚【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">美【大】，甚【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561006"><lem wit="【大】">美</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">甚</rdg></app>
<lb n="0561a11" ed="T"/>好，入中<note n="0561007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">洗＝洒【三】【宮】下同</note><note n="0561007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">洗【大】下同，洒【宋】【元】【明】【宮】下同</note><app n="0561007"><lem wit="【大】">洗</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">洒</rdg></app>浴，冀得涼樂，以除熱苦；方入其
<lb n="0561a12" ed="T"/>中，舉身爛壞，渴欲飲之，一口入咽，五藏焦
<lb n="0561a13" ed="T"/>爛，<note n="0561008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">飢＝肌【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">肌【CB】【麗-CB】【宋】【元】【明】【宮】，飢【大】</note><app n="0561008"><lem wit="【CB】【麗-CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">肌<note type="cf1">K19n0763_p0739c21</note></lem><rdg wit="【大】">飢</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">肌</rdg></app>肉離骨。何罪所致？」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0561a1310" rend="inline">答言：「汝為人時，好
<lb n="0561a14" ed="T"/>為相師，相人吉凶，少實多虛，或毀或譽，自稱
<lb n="0561a15" ed="T"/>有德，以動人心，以求利養。又於父母、兄弟、宗
<lb n="0561a16" ed="T"/>親諂偽不實，今受花報。果在地獄，<note n="0561009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">受苦億倍＝憂苦叵言【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">受苦億倍【大】，憂苦叵言【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561009"><lem wit="【大】">受苦億
<lb n="0561a17" ed="T"/>倍</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">憂苦叵言</rdg></app>，說不可<note n="0561010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">盡＋（也）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">盡【大】，盡也【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561010"><lem wit="【大】">盡</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">盡也</rdg></app>。」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0561a1706" rend="inline">一鬼問言：「我受身<note n="0561011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">以＝已【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">以【大】，已【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561011"><lem wit="【大】">以</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">已</rdg></app>來。常有
<lb n="0561a18" ed="T"/><note n="0561012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">惡＝一【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">惡【大】，一【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561012"><lem wit="【大】">惡</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">一</rdg></app>狗，體大牙利、兩目赫赤，晝夜常來而噉我
<lb n="0561a19" ed="T"/>身，命未盡頃肉<note n="0561013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">尋＝便【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">尋【大】，便【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561013"><lem wit="【大】">尋</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">便</rdg></app>復生，<note n="0561014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">復＝生【宮】</note><note n="0561014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">復【大】，生【宮】</note><app n="0561014"><lem wit="【大】">復</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">生</rdg></app>受此苦，痛不可
<lb n="0561a20" ed="T"/><note n="0561015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（堪）＋忍【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">忍【大】，堪忍【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561015"><lem wit="【大】">忍</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">堪忍</rdg></app>，何罪所致？」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0561a2006" rend="inline">答言：「汝為人時，作天<note n="0561016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">祠＝祀【宋】【元】【宮】＊</note><note n="0561016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">祠【大】＊，祀【宋】【元】【宮】＊</note><app n="0561016"><lem wit="【大】">祠</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【宮】">祀</rdg></app>主，
<lb n="0561a21" ed="T"/>於天<app type="star" corresp="#0561016"><lem wit="【大】">祠</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【宮】">祀</rdg></app>中，取牛羊血以祀於天，自食其肉，
<lb n="0561a22" ed="T"/>語眾人言：『汝等<note n="0561017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">祀天＝祠祀【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">祀天【大】，祠祀【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561017"><lem wit="【大】">祀天</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">祠祀</rdg></app>，大得吉利！』作<note n="0561018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">諸惡邪＝惡邪罪【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">諸惡邪【大】，惡邪罪【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561018"><lem wit="【大】">諸惡邪</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">惡邪罪</rdg></app>
<lb n="0561a23" ed="T"/>以惑百姓，今受花報，果在地獄。」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0561a2313" rend="inline">一鬼問言：「我
<lb n="0561a24" ed="T"/>受此身，常<note n="0561019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">在＝處【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">在【大】，處【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561019"><lem wit="【大】">在</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">處</rdg></app>不淨<note n="0561020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔中〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">中【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561020"><lem wit="【大】">中</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>，舉身塗漫，有所噉食
<lb n="0561a25" ed="T"/>皆是不淨，恒受此苦，不能得離，臭惱纏身，憂
<lb n="0561a26" ed="T"/>患叵計，何罪所致？」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0561a2608" rend="inline">答言：「汝為人時，作婆羅
<lb n="0561a27" ed="T"/>門，不信佛法，不樂供養沙門、道人，<note n="0561021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">若＝客【三】</note><note n="0561021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">若【大】，客【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0561021"><lem wit="【大】">若</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">客</rdg></app>來乞
<lb n="0561a28" ed="T"/>求，恒不欲見。時有一道人來從汝乞。汝作是
<lb n="0561a29" ed="T"/>念：『當作方便，令不復來。』即取鉢盛屎著下，以
<pb n="0561b" ed="T" xml:id="T17.0746.0561b"/>
<lb n="0561b01" ed="T"/>飯覆上，<note n="0561022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">將＝持【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">將【大】，持【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561022"><lem wit="【大】">將</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">持</rdg></app>與道人。<note n="0561023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔道人〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">道人【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561023"><lem wit="【大】">道人</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>得已，還至本處，持
<lb n="0561b02" ed="T"/>著一面，淨洗手訖，坐而執鉢，<note n="0561024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">手取欲食＝取飯食之【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">手取欲食【大】，取飯食之【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561024"><lem wit="【大】">手取欲食</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">取飯食之</rdg></app>，鉢
<lb n="0561b03" ed="T"/>中不淨，臭不可近。以是因緣，受此臭惱，今受
<lb n="0561b04" ed="T"/>花報，果在地獄，<note n="0561025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">常＝當【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">常【大】，當【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561025"><lem wit="【大】">常</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">當</rdg></app>吞<note n="0561026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔熱〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">熱【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561026"><lem wit="【大】">熱</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>鐵丸，身體爛壞，苦
<lb n="0561b05" ed="T"/>不可言。」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0561b0504" rend="inline">一鬼問言：「我受此身，處處舌出，有自
<lb n="0561b06" ed="T"/>然斧，而斬截之，如是無數，何罪所致？」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0561b0615" rend="inline">答言：
<lb n="0561b07" ed="T"/>「汝為人時，作小道人，為僧所差，取<note n="0561027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">冷＝清【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">冷【大】，清【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561027"><lem wit="【大】">冷</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">清</rdg></app>淨水，
<lb n="0561b08" ed="T"/>作石蜜漿，分與眾僧。石蜜堅大，打取少<note n="0561028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">許＋（而）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">許【大】，許而【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561028"><lem wit="【大】">許</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">許而</rdg></app>，
<lb n="0561b09" ed="T"/>盜<note n="0561029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">食＋（之）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">食【大】，食之【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561029"><lem wit="【大】">食</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">食之</rdg></app>一口。盜僧物故，今受<note n="0561b0901" resp="CBETA" type="add">花【CB】【麗-CB】，華【大】</note><app n="0561b0901"><lem wit="【CB】【麗-CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">花<note type="cf1">K19n0763_p0740b05</note></lem><rdg wit="【大】">華</rdg></app>報，果在地獄，
<lb n="0561b10" ed="T"/>吞<note n="0561030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">注＝於【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">注【大】，於【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561030"><lem wit="【大】">注</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">於</rdg></app>洋銅，苦不可<note n="0561031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">言＝說【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">言【大】，說【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561031"><lem wit="【大】">言</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">說</rdg></app>。」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0561b1009" rend="inline">一鬼問言：「我受此身，
<lb n="0561b11" ed="T"/>常苦飢餓，往至廁上，欲取屎食。廁上有大力
<lb n="0561b12" ed="T"/>鬼，以杖打我，初不得近，何罪所致？」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0561b1214" rend="inline">答言：「汝
<lb n="0561b13" ed="T"/>為人時，曾作道人，為佛圖主，悋護僧物，不以
<lb n="0561b14" ed="T"/>好食供養眾僧，常以麁惡與之。或時<note n="0561032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔時〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">時【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561032"><lem wit="【大】">時</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>欲作
<lb n="0561b15" ed="T"/>好食，<note n="0561033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（見）＋客【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">客【大】，見客【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561033"><lem wit="【大】">客</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">見客</rdg></app>比丘來，便止不作，待去乃設。惡心
<lb n="0561b16" ed="T"/>慳惜，今受花報，果在地獄。」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0561b1611" rend="inline"><note n="0561034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔一鬼…地獄〕六十七字－【宮】</note><note n="0561034a" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（一鬼…所致）二十八字【大】，〔－〕【宮】</note><app n="0561034a" cb:word-count="28"><lem wit="【大】">一鬼問言：「我受
<lb n="0561b17" ed="T"/>此身，腹大如甕，餘身分皆小，咽如<note n="0561035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔細〕－【三】</note><note n="0561035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">細【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0561035"><lem wit="【大】">細</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>針孔，
<lb n="0561b18" ed="T"/>不得下食，何罪所致？」</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></p><p xml:id="pT17p0561b1809" rend="inline"><note n="0561034b" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（答言…地獄）三十九字【大】，〔－〕【宮】</note><app n="0561034" cb:word-count="39"><lem wit="【大】">答言：「汝為人時，作聚落
<lb n="0561b19" ed="T"/>主，自恃豪強，<note n="0561036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">欺＋（凌）【三】</note><note n="0561036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">欺【大】，欺凌【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0561036"><lem wit="【大】">欺</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">欺凌</rdg></app>人民，常以無道索人飲食，
<lb n="0561b20" ed="T"/>以苦百姓，今受花報，果在地獄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0561b2013" rend="inline">一鬼問言：「我
<lb n="0561b21" ed="T"/>受此身，肩上有銅瓶，滿中洋銅，手捉一杓，以
<lb n="0561b22" ed="T"/>酌取之，自灌其頭，舉身焦爛，如是無數，苦痛
<lb n="0561b23" ed="T"/>無量，何罪所致？」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0561b2307" rend="inline">答言：「汝為人時，出家修道，
<lb n="0561b24" ed="T"/>知僧飲食，<note n="0561037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">以＝取【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">以【大】，取【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561037"><lem wit="【大】">以</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">取</rdg></app>一酥瓶，藏著餘處，客道人來
<lb n="0561b25" ed="T"/>而不與之，客去出<note n="0561038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">酥＋（瓶）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">酥【大】，酥瓶【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561038"><lem wit="【大】">酥</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">酥瓶</rdg></app>行與舊僧。此酥是招
<lb n="0561b26" ed="T"/>提僧物，一切有分，<note n="0561039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（以）＋隱【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">隱【大】，以隱【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561039"><lem wit="【大】">隱</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">以隱</rdg></app>匿僧物，與不平等。以
<lb n="0561b27" ed="T"/>是因緣，得如是苦，今受花報，果在地獄，<note n="0561040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">受苦＝苦痛【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">受苦【大】，苦痛【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561040"><lem wit="【大】">受
<lb n="0561b28" ed="T"/>苦</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">苦痛</rdg></app>難計。」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0561b2804" rend="inline">一鬼問言：「我受此身，常有人來，持
<lb n="0561b29" ed="T"/><note n="0561041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔諸〕－【宮】</note><note n="0561041" resp="CBETA" type="mod">諸【大】，〔－〕【宮】</note><app n="0561041"><lem wit="【大】">諸</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>刀鋸，<note n="0561042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">割剝＝剝刺【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561042" resp="CBETA" type="mod">割剝【大】，剝刺【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561042"><lem wit="【大】">割剝</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">剝刺</rdg></app>我身，又破<note n="0561043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">其＝我【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561043" resp="CBETA" type="mod">其【大】，我【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561043"><lem wit="【大】">其</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">我</rdg></app>腹，出其五藏，
<pb n="0561c" ed="T" xml:id="T17.0746.0561c"/>
<lb n="0561c01" ed="T"/>肉盡筋斷，痛不可<note n="0561044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">忍＋（受）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561044" resp="CBETA" type="mod">忍【大】，忍受【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561044"><lem wit="【大】">忍</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">忍受</rdg></app>。須臾之間，肉生平復，
<lb n="0561c02" ed="T"/>尋復來割，何罪所致？」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0561c0209" rend="inline">答言：「汝為人時，作婆
<lb n="0561c03" ed="T"/>羅門，不信正法，常生邪見，奉事天神，恒以牛
<lb n="0561c04" ed="T"/>羊禱<note n="0561045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">祠＝祀【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561045" resp="CBETA" type="mod">祠【大】，祀【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561045"><lem wit="【大】">祠</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">祀</rdg></app>，以是罪故，今<note n="0561046" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">受＋（此苦此是）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561046" resp="CBETA" type="mod">受【大】，受此苦此是【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561046"><lem wit="【大】">受</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">受此苦此是</rdg></app>花報，果在地獄。」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0561c0416" rend="inline">一
<lb n="0561c05" ed="T"/>鬼問言：「我受此身，常有人來，持諸刀鋸，割剝
<lb n="0561c06" ed="T"/>我身，又破其腹，出其五藏，肉盡筋斷，苦切叵
<lb n="0561c07" ed="T"/>忍。須臾之間，肉生平復，尋復來割，何罪所
<lb n="0561c08" ed="T"/>致？」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0561c0802" rend="inline">答言：「汝為人時，常作魁膾，主知殺人無有
<lb n="0561c09" ed="T"/>慈心，<note n="0561c0901" resp="CBETA" type="add">歡【CB】【麗-CB】，歎【大】</note><app n="0561c0901"><lem resp="CBETA.maha" wit="【CB】【麗-CB】">歡<note type="cf1">K19n0763_p0740c15</note></lem><rdg wit="【大】">歎</rdg></app>喜行之，有如是罪，<note n="0561047" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">故得此惡＝得此苦痛【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561047" resp="CBETA" type="mod">故得此惡【大】，得此苦痛【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561047"><lem wit="【大】">故得此惡</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">得此苦痛</rdg></app>，今受
<lb n="0561c10" ed="T"/>花報，果在地獄。」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0561c1007" rend="inline">一鬼問言：「我受此身，兩腋下
<lb n="0561c11" ed="T"/>恒有熱<note n="0561048" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">鐵＋（輪行時）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561048" resp="CBETA" type="mod">鐵【大】，鐵輪行時【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561048"><lem wit="【大】">鐵</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">鐵輪行時</rdg></app>輪轉，<note n="0561049" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">大＝火【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561049" resp="CBETA" type="mod">大【大】，火【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561049"><lem wit="【大】">大</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">火</rdg></app>熱逼身兩<note n="0561050" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">腋＋（下）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561050" resp="CBETA" type="mod">腋【大】，腋下【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561050"><lem wit="【大】">腋</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">腋下</rdg></app>焦爛，何罪
<lb n="0561c12" ed="T"/>所致？」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0561c1203" rend="inline">答言：「汝為人時，出家學道，與僧<note n="0561051" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔作〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561051" resp="CBETA" type="mod">作【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561051"><lem wit="【大】">作</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>種
<lb n="0561c13" ed="T"/>種餅，僧未下食，汝時貪心盜取僧餅，藏著腋
<lb n="0561c14" ed="T"/>下屏處食之，以是因緣得如是苦，今受花報，
<lb n="0561c15" ed="T"/>果在地獄，受苦難量。」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0561c1509" rend="inline">一鬼問言：「我受此身，常
<lb n="0561c16" ed="T"/>有自然赤鐵丸，從空中下，入口至腹，或<note n="0561052" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔從〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561052" resp="CBETA" type="mod">從【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561052"><lem wit="【大】">從</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>
<lb n="0561c17" ed="T"/>左出右入，<note n="0561053" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔或從〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561053" resp="CBETA" type="mod">或從【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561053"><lem wit="【大】">或從</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>右出左入，舉身焦爛，<note n="0561054" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔痛切〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561054" resp="CBETA" type="mod">痛切【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561054"><lem wit="【大】">痛切</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>
<lb n="0561c18" ed="T"/>無量，何罪所致？」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0561c1807" rend="inline">答言：「汝為人時，出家為
<lb n="0561c19" ed="T"/>沙彌，為僧煮菴羅果。僧中行之，至和上前，
<lb n="0561c20" ed="T"/><note n="0561055" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔輒〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561055" resp="CBETA" type="mod">輒【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561055"><lem wit="【大】">輒</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>長與七枚。以是因緣，<note n="0561056" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">得如是惡＝故得惡苦【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561056" resp="CBETA" type="mod">得如是惡【大】，故得惡苦【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561056"><lem wit="【大】">得如是惡</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">故得惡苦</rdg></app>，今受<note n="0561c2001" resp="CBETA" type="add">花【CB】【麗-CB】，華【大】</note><app n="0561c2001"><lem wit="【CB】【麗-CB】" resp="CBETA.maha">花<note type="cf1">K19n0763_p0741a06</note></lem><rdg wit="【大】">華</rdg></app>
<lb n="0561c21" ed="T"/>報，果在地獄。」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0561c2106" rend="inline">一鬼問言：「我受此身，意欲行來，
<lb n="0561c22" ed="T"/>發動迴還，猶如旋風，初不得前，愁惱悶苦，不
<lb n="0561c23" ed="T"/>可稱計，何罪所致？」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0561c2308" rend="inline">答言：「汝為人時，作卜問
<lb n="0561c24" ed="T"/>師，詭誑他人，令心<note n="0561057" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">罔＝幻【三】【宮】</note><note n="0561057" resp="CBETA" type="mod">罔【大】，幻【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0561057"><lem wit="【大】">罔</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">幻</rdg></app>惑，或喜或怖，皆不真
<pb n="0562a" ed="T" xml:id="T17.0746.0562a"/>
<lb n="0562a01" ed="T"/>實，由此因緣，得如是惡，今受花報，果在地獄。」</p>
<lb n="0562a02" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT17p0562a0201">一鬼問言：「我受此身，內常有熱，猶懷湯火，復
<lb n="0562a03" ed="T"/>來燒煮，苦痛萬端，何罪所致？」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0562a0312" rend="inline">答言：「汝為人
<lb n="0562a04" ed="T"/>時，作國王第一夫人。時王<note n="0562001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">貴＝偏【三】【宮】</note><note n="0562001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">貴【大】，偏【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0562001"><lem wit="【大】">貴</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">偏</rdg></app>敬小夫人，汝
<lb n="0562a05" ed="T"/>常生嫉心，作惡方便，求欲殺之。伺其臥時，煮
<lb n="0562a06" ed="T"/>酥令熱，注著腹上。其人得此苦痛無量，遂
<lb n="0562a07" ed="T"/><note n="0562002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">便＝致【三】【宮】</note><note n="0562002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">便【大】，致【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0562002"><lem wit="【大】">便</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">致</rdg></app>命終。由是因緣，得如是苦，今受花報，果
<lb n="0562a08" ed="T"/>在地獄。」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0562a0804" rend="inline">一鬼問言：「<note n="0562003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔言〕－【宋】【元】【宮】</note><note n="0562003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔－〕【CB】【麗-CB】【宋】【元】【宮】，言【大】</note><app n="0562003"><lem wit="【CB】【麗-CB】" resp="CBETA.maha"><space quantity="0"/><note type="cf1">K19n0763_p0741a19</note></lem><rdg wit="【大】">言</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>我受此身，性多恐怖，
<lb n="0562a09" ed="T"/>常畏人來，收閉繫縛、<note n="0562004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">枷鎖＝加諸【三】【宮】</note><note n="0562004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">枷鎖【大】，加諸【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0562004"><lem wit="【大】">枷鎖</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">加諸</rdg></app>楚毒，初無歡心，
<lb n="0562a10" ed="T"/>何罪所致？」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0562a1005" rend="inline">答言：「汝為人時，好行邪婬，犯人婦
<lb n="0562a11" ed="T"/>女，常畏發覺，心不自寧，今受花報，果在地獄，
<lb n="0562a12" ed="T"/>或臥鐵床或抱銅柱，如是之<note n="0562005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">苦＝罪【三】【宮】</note><note n="0562005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">苦【大】，罪【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0562005"><lem wit="【大】">苦</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">罪</rdg></app>，不可稱計。」</p>
<lb n="0562a13" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT17p0562a1301">一鬼問言：「我受此身，自然熱鐵，而有籠網，纏
<lb n="0562a14" ed="T"/>絡我身，燒熱焦爛，痛毒叵言，何罪所致？」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0562a1416" rend="inline">答
<lb n="0562a15" ed="T"/>言：「汝為人時，<note n="0562006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔常〕－【宮】</note><note n="0562006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">常【大】，〔－〕【宮】</note><app n="0562006"><lem wit="【大】">常</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>持<note n="0562007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">罝＝罥【三】，置【宮】</note><note n="0562007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">罝【大】，罥【宋】【元】【明】，置【宮】</note><app n="0562007"><lem wit="【大】">罝</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">罥</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">置</rdg></app>網，殺諸魚獸，籠取飛
<lb n="0562a16" ed="T"/>鳥。以是因緣，得如是苦切，今受花報，果在地
<lb n="0562a17" ed="T"/>獄。」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0562a1702" rend="inline">一鬼問言：「我受此身，無有手足，如一叚
<lb n="0562a18" ed="T"/>肉，在於曠野，狐狼虎豹，鵰鷲眾鳥，競來搏
<lb n="0562a19" ed="T"/>撮，爭共食之，苦痛叵言，何罪所致？」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0562a1914" rend="inline">答言：「汝
<lb n="0562a20" ed="T"/>為人時，作惡方便，若己若他，妊<note n="0562008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">身＝娠【元】【明】</note><note n="0562008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">身【大】，娠【元】【明】</note><app n="0562008"><lem wit="【大】">身</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">娠</rdg></app>之時，即
<lb n="0562a21" ed="T"/>便與藥，令胎消化。由是因緣，得如是苦，今受
<lb n="0562a22" ed="T"/>花報，果在地獄。」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0562a2207" rend="inline">又三鬼一時來問言：「我受此
<lb n="0562a23" ed="T"/>身，常有鐵釘，從空中下，釘我身上，入肌破
<lb n="0562a24" ed="T"/>骨，痛毒徹髓，何罪所致？」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0562a2410" rend="inline">答言：「汝為人時，一
<lb n="0562a25" ed="T"/>人作馬師，一人作牛師，一人作象師。苟貪他
<lb n="0562a26" ed="T"/>財，鍼刺無道，使受痛苦，而不除痛，由是因
<lb n="0562a27" ed="T"/>緣，得如是苦，今受花報，果在地獄。」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0562a2714" rend="inline">一鬼問言：
<lb n="0562a28" ed="T"/>「我受此身，無有頭首，眼耳鼻口，盡在胸前，何
<lb n="0562a29" ed="T"/>罪所致？」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0562a2904" rend="inline">答言：「汝為人時，若見殺人，與之捉
<pb n="0562b" ed="T" xml:id="T17.0746.0562b"/>
<lb n="0562b01" ed="T"/>頭，歡喜而挽，無有慈心。由是因緣，得如是
<lb n="0562b02" ed="T"/>身，今受花報，果在地獄。」</p><p xml:id="pT17p0562b0210" rend="inline">目連答諸鬼已，皆生
<lb n="0562b03" ed="T"/>敬心，走前懺悔。目連見其歡喜，更為說法。諸
<lb n="0562b04" ed="T"/>鬼聞已，皆大歡喜。</p></cb:div>
